name: David C Quates
pob: Herbert, Conecuh, Alabama, United States of America
bio: David C Quates was born on 13 June 1838, in Herbert, Conecuh, Alabama, United States. He married Susan Margaret Presley in 1860. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 7 daughters. He lived in Brooklyn, Conecuh, Alabama, United States in 1900 and Election Precinct 8 Jamestown, Conecuh, Alabama, United States in 1910. He registered for military service in 1907. He died in January 1929, in Travis Bridge, Conecuh, Alabama, United States, at the age of 90.
